folder: Fort Washington Aven & 186th Street, Manhattan, NY
text:
596-578 Fort Washington Ave., (rear view) at, adjoining and south of the S.E. corner of West 187th Street, as seen from Bennett Ave., at 186th Street. The 1-story buildings at the corner direct, are Nos. 596-592 inclusive; the apartment house Nos. 590-578.

November 23, 1930.
P.L.Sperr
title: Manhattan: Fort Washington Aven - 186th Street
